IN THE CIRCUIT COURT OF THE 15TH JUDICIAL CIRCUIT, IN AND FOR PALM BEACH COUNTY, FLORIDA
Case No.: 502006CF009454AXXXMB
STATE OF FLORIDA
v.
JEFFREY EPSTEIN,
Defendant
NOTICE OF WITHDRAWAL OF MOTION FOR PROTECTIVE ORDER
COMES NOW, Witness Y. Doe, by and through undersigned counsel, upon the representation of counsel for Defendant, Jeffrey Epstein, that he agrees to cancel the deposition of Y. Doe, hereby withdraws her Motion for Protective Order.
Dated: April 2, 2008
Respectfully submitted,
